latestPosts.caption:
sab pehno, mai bta rhi bad me bas regrets hi reh jayengi✨🎀

Trust me, the only thing you need is confidence. 💯

I’ve been in a very dark space where I literally stopped looking at myself because of how much weight I was losing. I rejected so many big opportunities, brand shoots, and events—just because I thought I was too skinny. It took me a very long time to understand that this is what I have now, and I can’t just sit back and ignore everything. Because let’s be real—this time, these opportunities—they don’t wait for you. They won’t come back. ⏳

I still regret saying No to one of the biggest brands for their product shoot. They even reached out twice, and now that I’m ready… it’s no longer there, waiting for me. 💔

Honestly, people can only make you feel bad about something if you let them. So wear that confidence like a crown 👑 and give it right back to them!
